                   "text": "The sum of the interior angles of a triangle is always _______ degrees.",
                   "type": "fill-in-blank",
                   "points": 5,
                   "difficulty": "easy",
                   "correctAnswer": "180",
                   "acceptableAlternatives": ["one hundred eighty"],
                   "explanation": "The sum of the interior angles of a triangle is a fundamental property of geometry, and it is always 180 degrees."
               }
           ]
       }
   ]
